放催淚煙。<br />\n<br />\n另外，組織表示，早前有年輕示威者在深水埗被捕後，警方拒絕讓社工提供支援及陪同前往警署，他們認為此舉嚴重剝奪對未成年被捕者的支援權利，絕不能夠接受。<br />\n<br />\n現場有數十人參與，又高叫口號，要求社署署長與在場人士公開對話<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUinobfi2nm8u4SjNJtTZF4Nk%3D&h=970230c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&h=0c818935\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n由今朝到0830到而家,署長話見又話有誠意。結果餓到我地而家係胡忠8樓,社署點解唔肯見社工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁你而家出黎未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae6139700246ad7f639245d4e5e47be8a62d214","tid":1518188,"uid":147803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:27:36.000Z","msg":"直選議席泛民多個建制"},{"pid":"4c62fc099c83105004a36babccaa23a0186c4117","tid":1518188,"uid":311962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ae6139700246ad7f639245d4e5e47be8a62d214","tid":1518188,"uid":147803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:27:36.000Z","msg":"直選議席泛民多個建制"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:28:08.000Z","msg":"意思是功能界別都是建制派取走？<br />\n點解？"},{"pid":"be431ade9cc062aee4f353020ffce9ead0e9fe24","tid":1518188,"uid":136988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c62fc099c83105004a36babccaa23a0186c4117","tid":1518188,"uid":311962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ae6139700246ad7f639245d4e5e47be8a62d214","tid":1518188,"uid":147803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:27:36.000Z","msg":"直選議席泛民多個建制"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:28:08.000Z","msg":"意思是功能界別都是建制派取走？<br />\n點解？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:29:55.000Z","msg":"老闆票,不是市民票"},{"pid":"5e76298d86b29